title: Core Tools CT126-LS-B Black Push Button Waterproof Switch
features: Perfect for Automotive, Motorcycle, ATV, or UTV electrical applications like lighting and accessories, this Push On, Push Off SPST switch also works great for most DC electrical projects
Waterproof Push Button Switch with Black Rubber Boot features 18 AWG 4.50 inch wire leads with 0.25 inch stripped end lengths
Constructed with high quality copper switch contacts and is rated for up to a 10 amp usage
Designed to mount in a 3/8 inch hole, allowing for a clean, professional look
Ideal for adding lights on a separate circuit from your stock lights, adding LED lighting, auxiliary spotlights, or switching a relay in higher power applications
description: Perfect for Automotive, Motorcycle, ATV, or UTV electrical applications like lighting and accessories, this Push On, Push Off SPST switch also works great for most DC electrical projects. Waterproof Push Button Switch with Black Rubber Boot features 18 AWG 4.50 inch wire leads with 0.25 inch stripped end lengths. Constructed with high quality copper switch contacts and is rated for up to a 10 amp usage. Designed to mount in a 3/8 inch hole, allowing for a clean, professional look. Ideal for adding lights on a separate circuit from your stock lights, adding LED lighting, auxiliary spotlights, or switching a relay in higher power applications. Please Note: The switch is not designed for heavy marine use or to be submersed under water. When installed properly it will endure most adverse weather conditions.
